==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Damned
<hw>Damned</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Sentenced
to punishment in a future state; condemned; consigned to
perdition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hateful; detestable; abominable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>But, O, what <qex>damned</qex> minutes tells he o'er⟦br⟧
Who doats, yet doubts, suspects, yet strongly loves.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Damnific</ent>⟦br⟧
